show.description: Kabhi brotherly love, toh kabhi deadly rivalry.Smith family ke andar ki duniya hai full-on twisted. Samantha ka sach ban gaya hai sabse bada threat. Iss kahani mein har pal hai suspense aur har rishta questionable. To abhi dekhna shuru kijiye.
